# Cursor Rules Template

> Create `.cursor/rules/` directory and add .mdc files for your rules.
> Below are templates for different types of rules.

---

## General Rules (general.mdc)

```markdown
---
description: General coding standards for the project
globs: ["**/*"]
alwaysApply: true
---

# Project Standards

## Code Quality
- Write self-documenting code with clear naming
- Keep functions focused (single responsibility)
- Limit function length to 30 lines
- Use meaningful variable names (no single letters except in loops)

## Error Handling
- Handle errors explicitly
- Provide meaningful error messages
- Log errors with context for debugging

## Documentation
- Document public APIs
- Add comments for complex logic
- Keep documentation up to date

## Security
- Never commit secrets
- Validate all external inputs
- Use parameterized queries
```

