## API Rules (api.mdc)

```markdown
---
description: API endpoint conventions
globs: ["**/api/**/*.ts", "**/routes/**/*.ts"]
alwaysApply: false
---

# API Standards

## Request Handling
- Validate all input using Zod or similar
- Return early on validation failures
- Use appropriate HTTP status codes
- Log request context for debugging

## Response Format
- Use consistent structure: { success, data?, error?, meta? }
- Include pagination metadata for lists
- Provide meaningful error messages
- Never expose internal errors to clients

## Security
- Verify authentication on protected routes
- Check authorization for resources
- Rate limit endpoints
- Sanitize output to prevent XSS
```

